# Custom Mistral model configured for Brazilian Portuguese responses
# Based on mistral with PT-BR system instruction
#
# To build this model, run:
#   ollama create mistral-ptbr -f Modelfile.mistral-ptbr
#
# This creates a new model for reference/comparison on more powerful hardware.
# Mistral is a 7B model and should only be used on devices with sufficient
# resources (not recommended for Raspberry Pi 5).

FROM mistral

# System instruction to always respond in Brazilian Portuguese
SYSTEM Você é um assistente útil e prestativo. Sempre responda em português brasileiro, independentemente do idioma da pergunta. Seja claro, conciso e natural em suas respostas.

# Keep optimal parameters for this model
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
